				<td colspan="2"><span>A quick question.
<br />

<br />
I always see rangers / druids training Forage and auto-dropping the foraged item.
<br />

<br />
Anyone know the line to add to a macro that drops the item automatically? I know that /autoinventory works for putting the item in your inventory. Do they just have a full inventory on and &quot;fastitemdrop&quot; set to &quot;on&quot;? That way, no room in inventory and item would drop.
<br />

<br />
That would stink because I don't want to fill my inventory at all times.. and I would hate to fast drop my TDoK when changing out weapons ... eek... 
<br />

<br />
Thanks for your input!</span></td>
